==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scyllite
<hw>Scyl"lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A
white crystalline substance of a sweetish taste, resembling inosite and
metameric with dextrose. It is extracted from the kidney of the dogfish
(of the genus <gen>Scyllium</gen>), the shark, and the skate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scymetar</ent>⟦br⟧
